## Available Classes

TWSX supports most Tailwind utility classes EXCEPT:

**❌ NOT SUPPORTED:**
- Responsive modifiers: `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`, `sm:`
- Pseudo-classes: `:hover`, `:focus`, `:active`
- Animations: `transition-*`, `duration-*`, `animate-*`
- Grid classes: `grid-cols-*`, `col-span-*` (use Grid component instead)

**✅ SUPPORTED:**

